  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bc2\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bcb\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcc\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1 \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "We are committed to continue to help Sri Lanka to meet its challenges - Indian President Draupadi Murmu's letter to President Ranil",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "As a close neighbour, Indian President Draupadi Murmu has said that India is committed to continuing to help the people of Sri Lanka to overcome the challenges caused by the economic crisis in line with the 'foreign first' policy.",
        "Draupadi Murmu, who has been elected as the President of the Republic of India, has said the above in his reply letter to the congratulatory letter sent by President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "'I thank you for the letter sent with your best wishes. Also, I congratulate you on being elected as the 8th President of Sri Lanka through Parliament.",
        "I wish you success in your responsibilities and challenges as you take up the high office at such an important moment in Sri Lanka.",
        "As a close neighbour, India is committed to continue to help the people of Sri Lanka to overcome the challenges posed by the economic crisis in line with its 'foreign first' policy.",
        "It is my hope that the long-standing bilateral partnership between our two countries will continue to grow stronger based on generations and deep people-to-people ties.' It is mentioned that"
      ],
